  "title": "Procurement Executive (MNC/ 5 Days / Up to $4,000 + AWS + Variable Bonus)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Position: Procurement Executive</strong></li><li><strong>Well Established Manufacturing MNC</strong></li><li><strong>Working Hours: Monday - Friday (8:30am – 6pm)</strong></li><li><strong>Salary (commensurate with experience): Up to $4,000 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Working Location: Kallang</strong></li><li><strong>Duration: Permanent</strong></li><li><strong>Industry: Manufacturing</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Main Responsibilities:</strong> </p><ul><li>Responsible for raw material sourcing by getting competitive quotes.</li><li>Accountable for supplier selection & component price data maintenance accuracy in SAP / Agile System.     </li><li>Drive & negotiate components pricing and control costs.</li><li>Build relationships with vendors and key suppliers.</li><li>Identify & develop potential suppliers.   </li><li>Execute analyses and make suggestions for improvement.    </li><li>Adhere to all relevant guidelines and regulations.</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma holder with technical background preferred.</li><li>At least 3 years’ experience in the EMS/Manufacturing environment.</li><li>Sourcing/Procurement experience in high mix low volume environment.</li><li>Proficient in SAP, Agile & Google workplace will be an added advantage.</li></ul><p>Email to: <strong>eugenie.cheah@ascension-sg.com</strong> for more information.</p><p><em>***We do not charge our candidates any referral fee nor bind them with any contract. ***</em></p><p>Eugenie Cheah<br />Consulting Manager<br />Reg no.: R24122293<br />EA No: 25C2861</p>",
