    "description": "<p>Empowering Businesses Through Integrated HR Solutions<br>\n<br>\nFounded in Singapore in 2025, Ascension Advisory Pte Ltd is a trusted human resource solutions provider committed to helping organizations enhance their HR and business operations. We offer a comprehensive suite of reliable and scalable HR services tailored to meet the unique needs of our clients.<br>\n<br>\nFrom inception to implementation, we partner closely with our clients, focusing on understanding their goals, developing effective strategies, and delivering high-quality solutions. Backed by the extensive knowledge and experience of our consultants, our mission is to drive long-term, sustainable results.<br>\n<br>\nOur Areas of Expertise:<br>\n1) Recruitment &amp; Executive Search<br>\n2) Foreign Manpower Solutions<br>\n3) Temporary &amp; Contract Manpower Solutions<br>\n4) Human Resource Advisory &amp; Consultancy<br>\n5) HR Business Process Outsourcing (BPO)<br>\n6) Learning &amp; Development Consultancy<br>\n7) Corporate &amp; Employee Insurance Consultancy<br>\n<br>\nLet us be your partner in building a stronger, more agile workforce.</p>",
